{"tid":1467754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日根本小事 都唔知輸咗啲乜","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:24:24.000Z","uid":25228,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"53b396441fc265f6453e4ba55fdd3e11d1df8385","tid":1467754,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"1. 阻旅客上機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母！唔阻都阻咗啦！係錯既咪認囉</span><br />\n仆街 阻咗啲旅客上機就好似世界末日咁係做乜鳩？肯認錯從來都係美德，仲同林奠、黑警既態度有極鮮明既對比<br />\n<br />\n2. 打人單野做咩要攬上身<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本冇人知打公安打假記者嗰班係咩人。</span> 狗隊二哥都講咗有狗仔混入示威者，根本冇人證明到打人嗰班係咪班狗扮架喎！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家狗隊誠信破產，點解會有連登仔覺得佢地會翻到身？今日檢討完之後唔該繼續去機場、繼續煲大721同811</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5407fad411c42e792823b1719a479cc45674b56","tid":1467754,"uid":60049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"整理思緖，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">818見</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KviyEOR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKviyEOR.gif&h=d2c73fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">認同請分享</code></pre>"},{"pid":"18923dfb318e3482974582cce47079c3259ca2cf","tid":1467754,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"和理非勇武同五大訴求一樣，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3506ef073fb552cad3c2e24b6869841f9a804673","tid":1467754,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"和理非勇武同五大訴求一樣，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6d5d47e19b5fd64d66eef94a198bb93845a750","tid":14